sentences: Christer-André Cederberg (born 22 May 1979) is a Norwegian mixer, music producer and the owner of Cederberg Studios.
This is what sparked his fascination for music production and lead him to becoming a full-time producer and engineer by 2001.

Christer played guitar in the band Animal Alpha in the period 2002 - 2009.
During the late 1990s he worked as a session musician, recording numerous albums.
